         LA    R4,L'MYHEAD1(R4)    BUMP TO NEXT LINE                            
*                                                                               
         CR    R4,R0               ROOM FOR ANY MORE?                           
         BNL   BH70                                                             
         CLC   0(L'MYHEAD1,R4),SPACES                                           
         BNE   BH70                                                             
         MVC   W,SPACES                                                         
         GOTO1 =V(GETUSER),DMCB,(C'S',ADCLT),(C'E',ADEST),(C':',W),0            
         TM    DMCB+4,CFLGSPQ+CFLGBHLQ   PRINT ON BILLING IN HEADLINES?         
