         CR    R4,R0               ROOM FOR ANY MORE?                           
         BNL   BH70                                                             
         CLC   0(L'MYHEAD1,R4),SPACES                                           
         BNE   BH70                                                             
         MVC   W,SPACES                                                         
         GOTO1 =V(GETUSER),DMCB,(C'S',ADCLT),(C'E',ADEST),0,(C':',W)            
