*                                                                               
* P1: KEY PASSED TO GETPROF                                                     
* P2: RETURNED PROFILE VALUES FROM GETPROF                                      
* P3: ADDITIONAL RETURNED INFO FROM GETPROF                                     
*                                                                               
         L     RF,APATCH                                                        
         TM    0(RF),X'10'         PRINT USER PROFILES?                         
         BZ    PRNTPRFX            NO                                           
