         MVC   P(PROFMSLQ),PROFMSG PREPARE TO PRINT PROFILE INFO                
         MVC   P(3),PROFKPGM                                                    
         TM    PROFKSYS,X'40'      SYSTEM IS LOWER CASE?                        
         BZ    *+14                                                             
         MVC   P(2),P+1            YES - PROGRAM IS 3 CHARS. LONG               
         MVI   P+2,C' '                                                         
         MVC   P+38(5),SPACES                                                   
         MVC   P+38(L'PROFIAGY),PROFIAGY                                        
