*                                                                               
*                                  FOR NETPAK THIS ROUTINE IS FOR               
*                                  FINDING MANUAL BILLS TO BE REVERSED          
*                                                                               
         CP    MANGRS,=P'0'        MANUAL BILL?                                 
         BNE   RNBX                YES - NO PREVIOUS                            
