         BE    RNB2                                                             
         CLI   CTYPQ,C'3'          'ALL TYPES'                                  
         BE    RNB2                                                             
         CLI   CTYPQ,C'1'          TIME/INTEG                                   
         BE    RNB2                                                             
         CLI   CTYPQ,C'T'          TIME ONLY                                    
         BNE   RNBX                                                             
