         MVC   KEY@.STABKAM,BAGYMD                                              
         MVC   KEY@.STABKCLT,BCLT                                               
         CLI   KPRD,0                                                           
         BE    RNB3                SKIP REST OF KEY NOW IF MULTI-PROD.          
         MVC   KEY@.STABKPRD,KPRD                                               
RNB2EST  DS    0H                                                               
         MVC   KEY@.STABKEST,BEST                                               
*                                                                               
RNB2MKT  DS    0H                                                               
         XC    KEY@.STABKMKT,KEY@.STABKMKT                                      
         XC    KEY@.STABKSTA,KEY@.STABKSTA                                      
         MVI   KEY@.STABKCUR,0                                                  
*                                                                               
RNB3     DS    0H                                                               
         GOTO1 HIGH                                                             
         B     RNB4B                                                            
RNB4     DS    0H                                                               
         GOTO1 SEQ                                                              
RNB4B    DS    0H                                                               
         CLC   KEY(5),KEYSAVE      AGM/CLIENT                                   
         BNE   RNB40                                                            
         CLI   KPRD,0                                                           
         BE    *+14                                                             
         CLC   KPRD,KEY@.STABKPRD  ONE PRODUCT MUST BE EQUAL                    
         BNE   RNB40                                                            
