         CLC   KEY@.STABKPRD,SAVPRD                                             
         BE    RNB5D                                                            
         MVC   SAVPRD,KEY@.STABKPRD                                             
*                                  GET PRODUCT ALPHA SEQ NO.                    
         L     RF,ADCLT                                                         
         LA    RF,CLIST-CLTHDR(RF)                                              
         LR    R0,RF                                                            
*                                                                               
         CLC   SAVPRD,3(RF)                                                     
         BE    *+12                                                             
         LA    RF,4(RF)                                                         
         B     *-14                                                             
*                                                                               
         SR    RF,R0                                                            
         SRL   RF,2                                                             
         STC   RF,BYTE2            SAVE PRODUCT SEQ NO.                         
*                                                                               
         CLI   QPGR,C' '           PGRS?                                        
         BE    RNB6                NO                                           
