         L     R2,PRDLIST                                                       
RNB5B    DS    0H                                                               
         CLC   KEY@.STABKPRD,5(R2)                                              
         BE    *+12                                                             
         LA    R2,6(R2)                                                         
         B     RNB5B                                                            
