         BH    RNB6                                                             
         OC    APGR1BRK,APGR1BRK                                                
         BZ    RNB6                                                             
         CLC   SAVPGR,BPGR+1       THEN CHECK RIGHT PGR                         
         BE    RNB6                YES                                          
*                                                                               
RNB5F    DS    0H                                                               
         ZIC   RF,KEY@.STABKPRD    BUMP TO NEXT PRODUCT                         
         AHI   RF,1                                                             
         STC   RF,KEY@.STABKPRD                                                 
         B     RNB2EST             SET KEY FROM ESTIMATE DOWN                   
