RNB6     DS    0H                  ESTIMATE                                     
         CLI   BEST,0                                                           
         BE    RNB6F                                                            
*                                  ONE ESTIMATE OR SERIES                       
         CLC   KEY@.STABKEST,BEST                                               
         BL    RNB2EST                                                          
         BE    RNB7                                                             
         CLI   BESTEND,0                                                        
         BE    RNB6D                                                            
         CLC   KEY@.STABKEST,BESTEND                                            
         BNH   RNB7                                                             
