         OC    APGR1BRK,APGR1BRK                                                
         BZ    RNB22B                                                           
         CLC   APGR1BRK,AINVBRK                                                 
         BH    *+10                                                             
RNB22A   DS    0H                                                               
         MVC   INVLPRD,STABKPRD                                                 
RNB22B   DS    0H                                                               
         CLC   AESTBRK,AINVBRK                                                  
         BH    *+10                                                             
         MVC   INVLEST,STABKEST                                                 
