         CLC   APERBRK,AINVBRK                                                  
         BH    *+10                                                             
         MVC   INVLPER,STABPER                                                  
         MVC   INVLSTA,XXSTA                                                    
         ICM   RE,15,STABGRS       CONVERT TO PCKD FOR INVLGRS                  
         CVD   RE,INVLGRS          GROSS                                        
         ICM   RE,15,STABNET                                                    
         CVD   RE,INVLNET          NET                                          
