         GOTO1 BINSRCH,INVPARS,(1,X)                                            
         OC    1(3,R1),1(R1)                                                    
         BNZ   *+6                                                              
         DC    H'0'                TABLE FULL                                   
         CLI   0(R1),1             ALREADY THERE                                
         BE    RNB12               NO - NEXT ELEMENT                            
