         MVC   ANXTPOS,AFRECP4     NEW RECORD                                   
         GOTO1 BLDREC,DMCB,=C'PR'                                               
         GOTO1 BLDREC,DMCB,(3,BEPRD)    CODE                                    
         GOTO1 BLDREC,DMCB,(24,BEPRDN)  NAME                                    
         MVC   X(8),SPACES              CODE IS ONLY 5 LONG,                    
         MVC   X(L'BEPRICD),BEPRICD     BUT EDI FIELD IS 8                      
