         GOTO1 BLDREC,DMCB,=C'MK'                                               
         GOTO1 BLDREC,DMCB,(4,BEMKT)   CODE                                     
         GOTO1 BLDREC,DMCB,(24,BEMKTN) NAME                                     
         BAS   RE,MFPUT                                                         
