         B     EDIX                                                             
         SPACE 2                                                                
***********************************************************************         
*        MFSTA - STATION                                                        
***********************************************************************         
*                                                                               
MFSTA    NTR1                                                                   
*                                                                               
         MVC   ANXTPOS,AFRECP4     NEW RECORD                                   
         GOTO1 BLDREC,DMCB,=C'ST'                                               
         GOTO1 BLDREC,DMCB,(9,BESTA)     CODE                                   
*                                  CITY AND AFF NOT USED FOR NETPAK             
         GOTO1 BLDREC,DMCB,(24,BESTCTY)  CITY                                   
         GOTO1 BLDREC,DMCB,(9,BESTAFF)   AFFILIATION                            
         BAS   RE,MFPUT                                                         
