*                                  TSAR RECORD TYPE EQUATES                     
EDHDRQ   EQU   10                                                               
EDAGMQ   EQU   20                                                               
EDADVQ   EQU   30                                                               
EDADDQ   EQU   32                                                               
EDPGRQ   EQU   40                                                               
EDPRDQ   EQU   50                                                               
EDESTQ   EQU   60                                                               
EDSTAQ   EQU   62                                                               
EDCOMQ   EQU   64                                                               
EDUSRQ   EQU   66                                                               
EDMGRQ   EQU   70                                                               
EDMKTQ   EQU   80                                                               
EDDUEQ   EQU   81                                                               
EDLSTQ   EQU   83                                                               
EDRMAQ   EQU   85                                                               
EDMTAQ   EQU   90                                                               
*                                  SORT SEQUENCE GROUPS                         
EDRSRTHQ EQU   10                  HEADER                                       
EDRSRTAQ EQU   15                  BILLING ADDRESS                              
EDRSRTMQ EQU   20                  MAIN                                         
