         L     RF,ADCLT            GET PRODUCT SEQ NO                           
         LA    RF,CLIST-CLTHDR(RF)                                              
         LR    R0,RF                                                            
         L     R6,NBAIO                                                         
*                                                                               
         CLC   NUPRD-NURECD(,R6),3(RF)                                          
         BE    *+12                                                             
         LA    RF,4(RF)                                                         
         B     *-14                                                             
*                                                                               
         SR    RF,R0                                                            
         SRL   RF,2                                                             
